title: 'ansi.ts: minimal ANSI escape code to HTML converter'
---
SGR sequences: 30-37 (fg colors), 90-97 (bright fg), 1 (bold), 0 (reset). State machine: tracks current fg color + bold. Output: span elements with inline style. No external deps. Handle partial sequences across chunk boundaries.